<view class="page route-list-page"><view wx:if="{{a}}" class="notice-bar warning" bindtap="{{b}}"><text class="notice-icon">⚠️</text><text class="notice-text">资质未完成审核，添加的线路不会对车商公开展示</text><text class="notice-action">去认证 ❯</text></view><view wx:if="{{c}}" class="segmented-control section"><view wx:if="{{d}}" class="{{['segment-item', e && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{f}}"> 大板轿运线路 </view><view wx:if="{{g}}" class="{{['segment-item', h && 'active']}}" bindtap="{{i}}"> 小板单车线路 </view></view><view wx:if="{{j}}" class="section empty-routes-card"><text class="empty-emoji">🛣️</text><text class="empty-text">暂无配置的承运线路</text><text class="empty-subtext">配置承运线路及报价时段，车商客户搜索该线路时将能直连联系您。</text><button class="primary-btn empty-btn" bindtap="{{k}}">立即添加线路</button></view><block wx:else><view wx:for="{{l}}" wx:for-item="route" wx:key="n" class="{{['section', 'route-card', route.o && 'closed']}}"><view class="row-between card-header"><view class="row align-center"><text class="route-badge">{{route.a}}</text><text class="{{['route-source-tag', 'font-bold', route.c]}}">{{route.b}}</text></view><text class="{{['status-tag', route.e]}}">{{route.d}}</text></view><view class="route-cities"><view class="city-name">{{route.f}}</view><text class="route-flow-arrow">⇄</text><view class="city-name">{{route.g}}</view></view><view class="route-meta-row row-between"><view class="route-meta-item"><text class="meta-label">预计时效: </text><text class="meta-val font-bold">{{route.h}}</text></view><view class="route-meta-item text-right"><text class="meta-label">托运参考价: </text><text wx:if="{{m}}" class="meta-price font-bold">{{route.i}}</text><text wx:else class="meta-price font-bold"> 起步价: {{route.j}}</text></view></view><view class="card-actions-row"><button wx:if="{{route.k}}" class="danger-btn card-mini-btn" bindtap="{{route.l}}"> 关闭展示 </button><button class="plain-btn card-mini-btn" bindtap="{{route.m}}">编辑报价</button></view></view></block><view class="floating-action-button" bindtap="{{n}}"><text class="fab-icon">+</text></view></view>